<br />
peix提到俺乡下的青口，俺就show一下它的模样：https://public.blu.livefilestore.com/y1pHKqNe66t1Q3bg4by39q63OaHKOTuJEYY44zVmcEdkKGocYqZjWKP-wq66r80sRrrAnw7Ly-fFuMduoDrti1_NQ/mussel.jpg?psid=1<br />
